@NODE intro "Intruduction"
@{JLEFT}
@{bold "Introduction"}

MeasConv is a Measurment Converter with MUI GUI.

Till now Supported measurments are:

For @{"Length" LINK lc} Conversion:

- Centimeter
- Kilometer (100000 Centimeters)
- Inch
- Foot
- Mile

For @{"Weight" LINK oc} Conversion:

- Kilograms
- Pounds

For @{"Temperature" LINK oc} Conversion:

- Celsuis Grades
- Fahreheit Grades
- Kelvin Grades

@{b}If in Your Country Are in Use some other Measurments for any of this
or some other type of Measurments notice me with.@{ub}How to do that see @{"Author" LINK author}
@ENDNODE
@NODE instal "Installation"
@{b}Installation@{ub}

Is very simple copy main program where you want ,copy
your prefered language catalog in LOCALE:catalog or keep it in
directory where is main program.

You Also Need @{"MUI" LINK mui} System Installed on Your Computer

@ENDNODE
@NODE req "Requirments"
@{bold "Requirments"}

This Program needs at least AmigaOS 2.04 or 2.1 (for locale support)
and @{"MUI" LINK mui} System (© Stefan Stuntz).
(I haven`t tryed on less then OS 3.0 but it should work)
@ENDNODE
